import React from "react";
import Button from "react-bootstrap/Button";

function Home() {

    <>
      <Row>
        <Col md={4}>
          <Card style={{ width: "18rem" }}>
            <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px180" />

        </Col>

        <Col md={4}>

              <Card.Text>
                Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up

              </Card.Text>

        </Col>
      </Row>
    </>
  );
}

export default Home;
